{"title":"Orto Delirium-2026","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría/Orto Delirium-2026.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"DELIRIUM (Síndrome\\NConfusional Agudo)","guid":"23iJZIfML0iBvhz_FtEKRg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición y Conceptos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"**Síndrome neuropsiquiátrico\\Ngrave** → inicio agudo de déficits\\Nen atención y cognición","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Etimología: latín *delirare*\\N→ \"salirse del surco\"","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Características cardinales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Alteración de atención → dirección,\\Nenfoque, mantenimiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"Alteración de conciencia →\\Norientación reducida al entorno","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"4","text":"**Fluctuación** → presencia y\\Nseveridad varían en el tiempo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"4","text":"Inicio agudo → horas a días","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"Duración: mayoría días, pero **~20%\\Npersiste semanas a meses**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Delirium subsindromático → algunas\\Ncaracterísticas sin criterios completos\\N(~2/3 AM hospitalizados)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"1","text":"Terminología\\Nconsensuada (10\\Nsociedades)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Delirium → estado clínico\\Ndefinido por DSM-5","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"Encefalopatía aguda → proceso\\Npatobiológico subyacente","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"EHpqc-6YI0qwDVyOKYpicA","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"Prevalencia por entorno","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Pacientes médicos hospitalizados →\\N**23%** (Meta-análisis 2020)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Postoperatorio cirugía\\Nmenor electiva → <10%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"Postoperatorio cirugía\\Nmayor/emergencia → **≥20%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"15","text":"Cirugía cardíaca (CABG) → **24%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"15","text":"TAVI transfemoral → 7.2% vs\\Notros abordajes 21.4%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"15","text":"Ictus agudo → **25%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"15","text":"UCI ventilados\\Nmecánicamente →\\N**50-70%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"15","text":"UCI general (ventilados + no\\Nventilados) → **31.8%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"15","text":"Cuidados paliativos hospital → 9-57%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"15","text":"Cuidados paliativos semanas\\Nprevias a muerte → **59-88%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"15","text":"Asilos/Nursing homes → 4.3-38%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"15","text":"Comunidad → **<2%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"15","text":"Fractura cadera →\\N**12-51%** (incidencia 17%)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"14","text":"Cirugía electiva → incidencia\\N**19%** (IC95% 16-23%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"14","text":"Cirugía emergencia → incidencia\\N**32%** (IC95% 25-39%)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"Subtipos Motores","guid":"rOww2paHX0iaP6WEYNEXQQ","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"**Hipoactivo** → ~50%","guid":"","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Peor pronóstico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"**Subdiagnosticado** →\\Nno esperar agitación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"Letargia, respuesta reducida","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"31","text":"Hiperactivo → ~25%","guid":"","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Agitación, hipervigilancia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Más fácil de reconocer","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"31","text":"Mixto → ~25%","guid":"","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"Alternancia entre estados","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"0","text":"Factores de Riesgo","guid":"PkrSdaFz2E-y0vC3UbF-RA","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Predisponentes (vulnerabilidad basal)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"**Edad avanzada** → mayor factor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"**Demencia/deterioro cognitivo** → FR\\Nindependiente más potente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"Bajo nivel educativo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"Alta carga de comorbilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"42","text":"**Fragilidad** (CFS ≥5)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"42","text":"Deterioro visual y auditivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"42","text":"Depresión/enfermedad psiquiátrica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"42","text":"Abuso de alcohol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"42","text":"Mala nutrición","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"42","text":"Uso previo opioides/benzodiacepinas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"42","text":"Historia previa de delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"42","text":"Neuroimagen: mayor atrofia cerebral,\\Nenfermedad sustancia blanca","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"41","text":"Precipitantes (estresores agudos)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Estrés quirúrgico → cardíaca, abdominal\\Nmayor, articulaciones, emergencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"Severidad enfermedad → sepsis,\\Nadmisión no planificada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"**Metabólicos**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"Deshidratación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"Hiponatremia/hipernatremia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"Lesión renal aguda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"58","text":"Disfunción hepática","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"58","text":"Hipoglucemia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"55","text":"Abstinencia alcohol/drogas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"55","text":"Neurológicos → convulsiones, ictus","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"55","text":"Fallo cardíaco","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"41","text":"Intrahospitalarios","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"**Dolor** no controlado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Infección nosocomial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Dispositivos invasivos\\N→ catéteres, vías","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"**Inmovilidad**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"67","text":"**Fármacos**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Opioides","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"**Polifarmacia**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"Benzodiacepinas →\\N\"veneno\" para el cerebro","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"**Anticolinérgicos** →\\Ncarga anticolinérgica >3","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"72","text":"Antihistamínicos 1ª generación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"72","text":"Corticoides","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"67","text":"Ambientales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"Privación de sueño","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"Desorientación día-noche","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"Falta comunicación familiar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"79","text":"**Restricciones físicas** →\\Nparadójicamente ↑ agitación","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"67","text":"UCI específicos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Sedación profunda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"Ventilación mecánica >96h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"84","text":"Infusiones benzodiacepinas","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"0","text":"Modelos Predictivos","guid":"R6clHwoBL06l-Lik6yssIQ","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"PRE-DELIRIC (UCI)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"10 factores a 24h de admisión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"**AUC 0.87 (IC95% 0.85-0.89)**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"Incluye: edad, APACHE-II, coma, infección,\\Nacidosis, sedantes, morfina, urea","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología\\N(Mecanismos\\NConvergentes)","guid":"jdH6arLAB0-l5balLbsRBQ","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"Concepto central → \"Fallo del cerebro\\Nvulnerable ante estresor agudo\"","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"Vulnerabilidad cerebral","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"Conectividad deteriorada por\\Nenvejecimiento/neurodegeneración","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"**Priming glial** → microglía\\Npreparada produce respuesta\\Ninflamatoria exagerada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"Cambios vasculares →\\Nalteración perfusión, fugas BHE","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"93","text":"Metabolismo energético (Hipótesis\\Ninsuficiencia metabólica)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"Hipoxia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Flujo sanguíneo cerebral\\N**↓30-50%** durante delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"Lactato LCR elevado en\\Nfractura cadera + delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"Hipoxia experimental →\\Nenlentecimiento EEG precede\\Nconfusión","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"104","parent":"99","text":"Alteración glucosa","guid":"","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"Hipoglucemia →\\Nenlentecimiento EEG","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"Resistencia insulina\\N(sepsis/cirugía) → ↓ captación\\Nglucosa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"104","text":"FDG-PET → hipometabolismo\\Nglucosa durante delirium","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"93","text":"Inflamación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Sistémica → sepsis, cirugía,\\Ntrauma liberan IL-1β, TNF, IL-6","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"Cerebral → activación\\Nendotelio, secreción PGE2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"Microglía primed → respuesta\\Nexagerada IL-1β, NO, ROS","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"Datos clínicos → PCR, IL-6, TNF\\Nelevados ↑ riesgo delirium","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"93","text":"Neurotransmisores","guid":"","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"**Acetilcolina ↓** →\\Nanticolinérgicos causan\\Ndelirium","guid":"","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"Inhibidores AChE **NO**\\Nprevienen/tratan (sin demencia)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"Dopamina → teoría\\Nhiperdopaminérgica\\Nsocavada","guid":"","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"Antipsicóticos fallan en\\Nprevención/tratamiento","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"113","text":"GABA ↑ → benzodiacepinas\\Ndeterioran cognición","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"113","text":"Noradrenalina ↑ → estrés/sepsis\\Ninterrumpe función prefrontal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"93","text":"Fallo conectividad redes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"Pérdida integridad cuerpo\\Ncalloso, sustancia blanca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"Reducción eficiencia global red","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":"Desconexión ejecutiva central ↔\\Nred neuronal por defecto","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"Moeme_tuBEyJqeQEdmLnHA","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"Criterios DSM-5","guid":"","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"A: Alteración atención + conciencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"B: Inicio agudo, cambio\\Nbasal, **fluctúa**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"C: Alteración cognitiva adicional\\N(memoria, lenguaje, percepción)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"D: No explicado por otro trastorno\\Nneurocognitivo ni coma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"125","text":"E: Consecuencia fisiológica\\Ndirecta de condición médica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"124","text":"Herramientas validadas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"**4AT** (práctica clínica general)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"4 componentes: Alerta, AMT4, Atención\\N(meses al revés), Cambio agudo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"Puntuación ≥4 → posible delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"**S 88%, E 88%**\\N(Meta-análisis N=3701)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"131","text":"**CAM** (Confusion\\NAssessment Method)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"Requiere: Criterio 1 (inicio agudo/fluctuante) + 2\\N(inatención) + [3 (pensamiento desorganizado) O\\N4 (nivel conciencia alterado)]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"S 0.09-1.0 (depende\\Nentrenamiento), E 0.84-1.0","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"131","text":"**3D-CAM** → variante 3 minutos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"131","text":"**CAM-ICU**\\N(ventilados y no\\Nventilados)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"Adaptación no verbal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"**S 80%, E 96%** (Meta-análisis)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"131","text":"**ICDSC** (UCI)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"Checklist 8 ítems","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"Score ≥4 → delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"**S 74%, E 82%**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"131","text":"**UB-2** (Ultra-brief)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"1. Día de la semana","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"2. Meses al revés","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"147","text":"Falla uno → sospechar","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"124","text":"Severidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"CAM-S → 0-7 (corta) o 0-19 (larga)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"151","text":"DRS-R98 →\\Nfenomenológica y\\Nseveridad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"151","text":"MDAS → 0-30 puntos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"124","text":"Investigaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"TAC cerebral → NO rutinario (solo 11%\\Npositivos, mayoría hemorragia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"EEG → si sospecha estatus\\Nepiléptico no convulsivo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"Hallazgos: enlentecimiento\\Noccipital, ↑ delta/theta, ↓ alfa","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"0","text":"Outcomes y Consecuencias","guid":"2MAdwnNm_UuOEUDNXe34Ww","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"Mortalidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"Asociación independiente con\\N↑ mortalidad post-alta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"Cirugía electiva","guid":"","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"1 mes: **OR 6.60**\\N(IC95% 1.58-27.66)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"6 meses: **OR 5.69**\\N(IC95% 2.33-13.88)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"162","text":"1 año: **OR 2.87** (IC95% 1.63-5.06)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"160","text":"Cirugía emergencia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"1 mes: **OR 3.56**\\N(IC95% 1.77-7.15)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"6 meses: **OR 2.60**\\N(IC95% 1.88-3.61)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"1 año: **OR 2.30** (IC95% 1.77-3.00)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"159","text":"Institutionalización → **RR 5.6**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"159","text":"Costos → **1.6-1.8 billones USD**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"159","text":"**Demencia incidente** (población ≥85a)\\N→ **OR 8.7** (IC95% 2.1-35)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"159","text":"**Aceleración demencia existente** →\\N**OR 3.1** (IC95% 1.5-6.3)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"159","text":"Riesgo demencia post-delirium → **OR\\N12.52** (Witlox JAMA 2010)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"159","text":"Deterioro cognitivo largo plazo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"Meta-análisis 23 estudios → Hedges' g\\N**0.45** (IC95% 0.34-0.57)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"**~20% persisten\\Nsíntomas a 6 meses**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"175","text":"Hasta **2/3** pacientes con\\Ndeterioro sustancial a 12 meses","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"159","text":"Impacto cognitivo diferencial","guid":"","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"Pacientes SIN deterioro cognitivo previo →\\N**mayor caída** si hacen delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"CDR-SB: **B 0.8\\Npuntos/año, P=0.012**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"179","text":"Teoría reserva cognitiva → más margen\\Npara empeorar visiblemente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"159","text":"Salud mental → ↑\\Ndepresión, ansiedad, TEPT","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"159","text":"Estado funcional →\\Ndeclive, discapacidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"0","text":"Prevención (Más efectiva\\Nque tratamiento)","guid":"-Pso1UU5yE-ldxO7GYhK1w","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"Intervenciones multicomponentes\\N→ **evidencia sólida**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"HELP (Hospital Elder Life Program)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"Aborda: deterioro visual/auditivo,\\Ninmovilidad, desorientación,\\Nprivación sueño, deshidratación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"**Reducción absoluta riesgo 5%**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"186","text":"Meta-análisis 2020 → **RR 0.\\N53** (IC95% 0.41-0.69)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"186","text":"Reducción incidencia **27-54%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"186","text":"También ↓ caídas,\\Núlceras por presión","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"185","text":"Medidas no\\Nfarmacológicas\\Nespecíficas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"Reorientación frecuente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"**Movilización temprana**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"Uso gafas/audífonos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"193","text":"Higiene del sueño (no farmacológica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"193","text":"Hidratación/Nutrición","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"193","text":"Manejo dolor (evitando\\Nopioides si posible)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"193","text":"**Evitar restricciones\\Nfísicas y catéteres**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"193","text":"Involucramiento familiar","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"185","text":"Bundle **ABCDEF** (UCI)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"A: Assess/manage pain\\N(evaluar/manejar dolor)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"B: Both awakening + breathing trials","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"C: Choice of analgesia/sedation","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"D: Delirium (evaluar,\\Nprevenir, manejar)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"202","text":"E: Early mobility (movilidad temprana)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"202","text":"F: Family involvement","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"202","text":"Cumplimiento → **aOR 0.60** (IC95% 0.\\N49-0.72) delirium día siguiente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"185","text":"Prevención farmacológica →\\N**evidencia negativa**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"Antipsicóticos (haloperidol, atípicos)\\N→ **NO** recomendados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"210","text":"Melatonina → resultados mixtos,\\Nsin evidencia consistente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"210","text":"Inhibidores colinesterasa\\N→ **NO** efectivos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"214","parent":"185","text":"EEG procesado (pEEG)\\Nguiado en anestesia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"Incidencia pEEG 19.\\N0% vs usual 23.3%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"214","text":"OR pooled **0.78** (IC95%\\N0.60-1.00, P=0.054)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"sVabdvfHxE6wLrCVM0xgFQ","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"Base del manejo → multidominio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":"Tratar causas precipitantes\\N(infección, metabólico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"218","text":"**Revisión medicación** →\\NSTOPP/START, deprescripción","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"218","text":"Manejo del distrés","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"218","text":"Mitigar complicaciones","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"223","parent":"217","text":"Farmacológico → **NO efectivo\\Npara tratar delirium per se**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"**Antipsicóticos**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"Estudio MIND-USA (2018 NEJM)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"Haloperidol vs\\NZiprasidona vs\\NPlacebo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"225","text":"**NO diferencias** en días\\Nlibres delirium/coma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"225","text":"Mediana: 8.5 vs 8.0 vs 8.0 días","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"224","text":"Recomendación SCCM PADIS →\\N**NO usar rutinariamente**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"224","text":"Excepción: distrés intratable, agitación\\Nsevera amenaza seguridad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"224","text":"Si uso → dosis mínima efectiva","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"232","parent":"223","text":"**Inhibidores AChE (Rivastigmina)** →\\N↑ mortalidad → **NO usar**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"223","text":"**Dexmedetomidina** (agonista α2)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"Mecanismo: sedación que imita sueño\\Nnatural, ↓ tono noradrenérgico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"233","text":"Mejor que benzodiacepinas/propofol →\\N↓ prevalencia delirium UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"233","text":"SPICE III → más días\\Nlibres delirium/coma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"233","text":"Indicación: ventilados donde\\Nagitación impide extubación","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"238","parent":"217","text":"Intervenciones no\\Nfarmacológicas para\\Ntratamiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"239","parent":"238","text":"Efectividad limitada\\Nuna vez instaurado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"238","text":"Multicomponente →\\Ninconsistente en\\Nduración/severidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"238","text":"Musicoterapia → RR 0.52 (IC95% 0.20-1.\\N35) modelo efectos aleatorios","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"242","parent":"217","text":"TO en UGA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"Prevención síndromes confusionales → terapia\\Norientación realidad (3h/semana)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"242","text":"Estimulación cognitiva\\Nsegún historia de vida","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"245","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGeriátricas Especiales","guid":"-JejZqfLW0ivLvTWmhqIrQ","children":[{"id":"246","parent":"245","text":"Demencia → mayor FR independiente","guid":"","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"Paciente con demencia que empeora =\\Ndelirium hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"248","parent":"245","text":"Fragilidad → predictor\\Noutcomes en UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"245","text":"Farmacocinética alterada\\Nen anciano crítico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"245","text":"Delirium en UCI","guid":"","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"Preferir dexmedetomidina\\Nsobre benzodiacepinas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"250","text":"Evitar sedación profunda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"250","text":"Evaluación CAM-ICU diario todo >65a","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"245","text":"Transiciones cuidado","guid":"","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"UCI → sala → domicilio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"254","text":"Seguimiento cognitivo\\Npost-alta necesario","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"245","text":"Criterios STOPP relevantes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"Anticolinérgicos en delirium/demencia →\\Nriesgo empeoramiento cognición","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"Neurolépticos como hipnóticos (salvo\\Npsicosis) → riesgo confusión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"257","text":"Benzodiacepinas →\\Nevitar uso crónico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas ⭐","guid":"oQXygv0W7Eu2lNbu4pMdbA","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"Diagnóstico es CLÍNICO → usar 4AT o\\NCAM, no confiar en \"impresión\"","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"261","text":"**Hipoactivo = buscar\\Nactivamente** → más frecuente,\\Npeor pronóstico, infradiagnosticado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"261","text":"Prevención es el ÚNICO \"tratamiento\"\\Nprobado → una vez instaurado, no\\Nhay fármaco que cure","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"261","text":"**Antipsicóticos ≠ tratamiento del\\Ndelirium** → solo si agitación severa\\Ncompromete seguridad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"261","text":"Buscar causas múltiples → no\\Ndetenerse en ITU; revisar deshidratación,\\Nestreñimiento, dolor, fármacos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"261","text":"**Benzodiacepinas = \"veneno\"** → solo en\\Nabstinencia alcohol/sedantes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"261","text":"Dolor induce delirium PERO opioides\\Ntambién → analgesia multimodal, no\\Ndejar sin analgesia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"261","text":"Estado mental = **6° signo vital**\\N→ cambio agudo en atención es\\Nemergencia médica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"261","text":"Paciente cognitivamente \"sano\"\\Nque hace delirium → **mayor\\Ncaída cognitiva a 1 año**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"261","text":"Educación familiar → \"fallo cerebral agudo\", no\\Ndemencia permanente ni locura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"261","text":"Restricciones físicas →\\Nparadójicamente **↑ agitación y\\Nlesiones** → último recurso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"261","text":"CAM-ICU diario en todo\\Npaciente UCI >65 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"261","text":"Al alta → advertir riesgo deterioro cognitivo\\Npersistente, planificar seguimiento","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"275","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"dUeU8BxncE6gDTfCmmrhfg","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"1. Wilson JE, Mart MF,\\NCunningham C, et al. Delirium. Nat\\NRev Dis Primers. 2020;6(1):90.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"2. Umoh M, Sharma A, Leoutsakos J, et al. Cognitive\\NOutcomes After Hip Fracture Surgery. Am J Geriatr\\NPsychiatry. 2025 (In Press).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"275","text":"3. Zhao Q, Liu S, Zhao H, et al. Non-pharmacological\\Ninterventions to prevent and treat delirium in older people.\\NInt J Nurs Stud. 2023;148:104584.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"275","text":"4. Yan E, Veitch M, Saripella A, et al. Association\\Nbetween postoperative delirium and adverse outcomes.\\NJ Clin Anesth. 2023;90:111221.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"275","text":"5. Sumner M, Deng C, Evered L, et al. Processed\\NEEG-guided anaesthesia to reduce POD. Br J\\NAnaesth. 2022;130(2):e243-e253.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"275","text":"6. Ministerio de Salud Chile.\\NOrientación Técnica UGA. 2023.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"275","text":"7. O'Mahony D, et al. STOPP/START\\Ncriteria version 3. Age Ageing. 2023.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"275","text":"8. American Geriatrics Society. Beers\\NCriteria. J Am Geriatr Soc. 2023.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":283,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría","filename":"Orto Delirium-2026","id":"map_1527","resolved_references":[]}